---- MODULE CompatibilityCheck ----
\* Bidirectional compatibility comparison between two IR schemas, producing a transport class result.
\* Generated by tlaiser — https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

\* State constants — each represents a distinct state
CONSTANTS Idle, Comparing, Concorde, BusinessClass, Economy, Wheelbarrow, Incompatible

\* Variables tracked by this specification
VARIABLES state, loss_count

\* Type invariant: state is always one of the declared states
TypeInvariant == state \in {Idle, Comparing, Concorde, BusinessClass, Economy, Wheelbarrow, Incompatible}

\* Initial state predicate
Init ==
    /\ state = Idle
    /\ loss_count = 0

\* Transition actions
\* Transition: Idle -> Comparing (start_compare)
start_compare ==
    /\ state = Idle
    /\ state' = Comparing
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: Comparing -> Concorde (zero_loss_full_fidelity)
zero_loss_full_fidelity ==
    /\ state = Comparing
    /\ loss_count = 0
    /\ state' = Concorde
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: Comparing -> BusinessClass (minor_loss_only)
minor_loss_only ==
    /\ state = Comparing
    /\ loss_count > 0
    /\ state' = BusinessClass
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: Comparing -> Economy (moderate_loss)
moderate_loss ==
    /\ state = Comparing
    /\ loss_count > 0
    /\ state' = Economy
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: Comparing -> Wheelbarrow (major_loss_but_viable)
major_loss_but_viable ==
    /\ state = Comparing
    /\ loss_count > 0
    /\ state' = Wheelbarrow
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: Comparing -> Incompatible (schemas_incompatible)
schemas_incompatible ==
    /\ state = Comparing
    /\ state' = Incompatible
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: Concorde -> Idle (reset)
reset ==
    /\ state = Concorde
    /\ state' = Idle
    /\ loss_count := 0
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: BusinessClass -> Idle (reset)
reset ==
    /\ state = BusinessClass
    /\ state' = Idle
    /\ loss_count := 0
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: Economy -> Idle (reset)
reset ==
    /\ state = Economy
    /\ state' = Idle
    /\ loss_count := 0
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: Wheelbarrow -> Idle (reset)
reset ==
    /\ state = Wheelbarrow
    /\ state' = Idle
    /\ loss_count := 0
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Transition: Incompatible -> Idle (reset)
reset ==
    /\ state = Incompatible
    /\ state' = Idle
    /\ loss_count := 0
    /\ UNCHANGED loss_count

\* Next-state relation: disjunction of all transitions
Next ==
    \/ start_compare
    \/ zero_loss_full_fidelity
    \/ minor_loss_only
    \/ moderate_loss
    \/ major_loss_but_viable
    \/ schemas_incompatible
    \/ reset
    \/ reset
    \/ reset
    \/ reset
    \/ reset

\* All variables tuple (for stuttering)
vars == <<state, loss_count>>

\* Complete specification
Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_vars

\* Fair specification (with weak fairness on Next)
FairSpec == Spec /\ WF_vars(Next)

\* ---- Temporal Properties ----
\* Property: SquisherInvariant (safety)
SquisherInvariant == []([](CompatibilityCheck = Incompatible => loss_count >= 0))

\* Property: ConcrodeImpliesNoLoss (safety)
ConcrodeImpliesNoLoss == []([](CompatibilityCheck = Concorde => loss_count = 0))

\* Property: AnalysisEventuallyCompletes (liveness)
AnalysisEventuallyCompletes == <>(<>(SchemaAnalysis = Parsed \/ SchemaAnalysis = AnalysisFailed))


====
